tool_description:
TikTok Data API
Get very useful information from TikTok.
name: TikTok Data
title: TikTok Data

api_list.name: User Profile Metadata
api_list.description: Get useful information about any user on TikTok!
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://tiktok-data.p.rapidapi.com/user/charlidamelio"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "tiktok-data.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
